content: <articles>    <article xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink/">   <front>     <article-meta>       <title-group>         <article-title>Module Data for the Empirical Investigation of Subsumption Test Hardness in Description Logic Classification</article-title>       </title-group>       <contrib-group>         <contrib contrib-type="author">           <name>             <surname>Parsia</surname>             <given-names>Bijan</given-names>           </name>           <aff>             <institution>University of Manchester</institution>           </aff>         </contrib>         <contrib contrib-type="author">           <name>             <surname>Sattler</surname>             <given-names>Uli</given-names>           </name>           <aff>             <institution>University of Manchester</institution>           </aff>         </contrib>         <contrib contrib-type="author">           <name>             <surname>Matentzoglu</surname>             <given-names>Nicolas</given-names>           </name>           <aff>             <institution>University of Manchester</institution>           </aff>         </contrib>       </contrib-group>       <pub-date pub-type="pub">         <year>2015</year>       </pub-date>       <self-uri xlink:href="http://zenodo.org/record/15682"/>       <self-uri xlink:href="https://zenodo.org/record/15682/files/cade2015_modules.zip"/>     </article-meta>     <abstract><p>This dataset contains 224 modules of 14 distinct ontologies for the submission &quot;Empirical Investigation of Subsumption Test Hardness in Description Logic Classification&quot; to CADE, 2015. The submitted version with the dataset description can be found here:</p>  <p>http://owl.cs.manchester.ac.uk/publications/supporting-material/subtest-hardness-in-classification/</p>  <p>The ontologies in this set are BioPortal ontologies from the snapshot provided at http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.15667.&nbsp;</p>  <p>The following ontologies are in the set:&nbsp;</p>  <p>MFOEM - Emotion Ontology<br /> BT - Biotop Ontology<br /> NEMO - Neural Electromagnetic Ontology<br /> NTDO - Neglected Tropical Disease Ontology<br /> OBI - Ontology for Biomedical Investigations<br /> OGSF - Ontology for Genetic Susceptibility Factor<br /> ONL-MSA - Mental State Assemssment<br /> VSO - Vital Sign Ontology<br /> CAO - Clusters of Orthologous Groups Cog Analysis Ontology&nbsp;<br /> ICO - Informed Consent Ontology<br /> OMRSE - Ontology of Medically Related Social Entities<br /> STATO - Statistics Ontology<br /> NPO - Nanoparticle Ontology<br /> OBCS - Ontology of Biological and Clinical Statistics</p></abstract>   </front>   <article-type>provisional-user-ontologycollections</article-type> </article>   </articles>
